
limiter [options] program [args]

    Run <program> and regularly check that it doesn't exceed
    given CPU time and resident set size limits (taking all its
    offspring into account)

    Options:
      -m <megabytes>     limit per-offspring memory usage (default 1GB)
      -t <milliseconds>  limit per-offspring cpu time (default 1 hour)
      -M <megabytes>     limit global memory usage (default 1GB)
      -T <milliseconds>  limit global cpu time (default 1 hour)
      -i <interval>      sampling interval (default 100ms)
